10 oddball American rock classics

Download or stream these psychedelic classics for free. All you’ll need is you library card and PIN.

  1. Looser for you Baby by Dr John from American Legend Vol. 1

  2. Monk Time by The Monks from The Early Years 1964-1965

  3. Levitation by The 13th Floor Elevators from The Psychedelic World Of

  4. You Yesyesyes Again by The Residents from Fingerprince

  5. Skunk (Sonically Speaking) by MC5 from The Anthology 1965–1971

  6. Sure ‘Nuff ‘N Yes I Do by Captain Beefheart and the Magic Band from The Buddah Years

  7. Mustang Sally by Silver Apples from The Garden

  8. In-A-Gadda-Da-Vida (full album version) by Iron Butterfly from In-A-Gadda-Da-Vida

  9. Dixie Chicken (Live) by Little Feat from Hellzapoppin

  10. Walkin’ Blues by Hot Tuna from Original Album Classics
